# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# SQL Database Analysis Tool — Environment Variables Template
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy this file to .env or backend/.env and fill in all CHANGE_ME values before running.
# NEVER commit your actual .env to version control.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Application ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
APP_NAME="DataPilot AI"
APP_ENV=development
APP_HOST=0.0.0.0
APP_PORT=8000
API_PREFIX="/api/v1"
DEBUG=true
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
LOG_FOLDER="logs"

# ── Target Databases to Analyze ───────────────────────────────────────────────
MYSQL_HOST=localhost
MYSQL_PORT=3306
MYSQL_USER=root
MYSQL_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password_here
MYSQL_DATABASE=your_database_name_here

POSTGRES_HOST=localhost
POSTGRES_PORT=5432
POSTGRES_USER=postgres
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=your_postgres_password_here
POSTGRES_DATABASE=your_database_name_here

# ── Backend Database (PostgreSQL for internal state) ──────────────────────────
POSTGRES_DB=sql_analytics
POSTGRES_USER=analytics_user
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_STRONG_DATABASE_PASSWORD
DB_HOST_PORT=5432
DB_POOL_SIZE=10
DB_MAX_OVERFLOW=20
DB_POOL_TIMEOUT=30
DB_ECHO=false

# ── Internal Database (SQLite/Query History) ──────────────────────────────────
ALLOWED_DATABASES="mysql,postgresql"
INTERNAL_DB_URL="sqlite:///./sql_tool.db"

# ── Redis ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_REDIS_PASSWORD
REDIS_HOST_PORT=6379

# ── JWT Security ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generate with: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"
JWT_SECRET_KEY=CHANGE_ME_JWT_SECRET_MINIMUM_32_CHARACTERS_LONG
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=10080
JWT_REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS=7

# ── CORS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:80
CORS_ORIGINS="http://localhost:3000,http://localhost:8501"

# ── Query Execution Limits ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
QUERY_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30
MAX_RESULT_ROWS=10000
MAX_JOINS_ALLOWED=5
MAX_QUERY_LENGTH_CHARS=5000

# ── Export Limits ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MAX_EXPORT_ROWS=50000
MAX_EXPORT_SIZE_MB=50
EXPORT_FOLDER="exports"

# ── AI API Keys ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
LLM_PROVIDER=openai
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
NVIDIA_API_KEY=your_nvidia_api_key_here

# ── Port Mapping ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
BACKEND_HOST_PORT=8000
FRONTEND_HOST_PORT=3000
NGINX_HTTP_PORT=80
NGINX_HTTPS_PORT=443

# ── Frontend ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NODE_ENV=production
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost/api